&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;About Us&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At &lt;strong&gt;We.&lt;/strong&gt;, we&#39;ve spent decades at the intersection of technology and humanity, bridging the gap between what businesses create and how people experience those creations. We&#39;ve learned that beneath even the most unruly situations — whether it&#39;s a global crisis, an emerging technology, or a sweeping organizational change—lies a simple human need. That need could be for trust, connection, safety, or a sense of purpose. But it’s always there. And it is only by uncovering these truths that we can make real, meaningful progress.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do you read STAT and NYT in one sitting? Would you like to be on the forefront of what’s next in health and health technology? And, most importantly, would you like to help our clients tell their health and tech stories in bold, unconventional ways?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our team sits at the intersection of profound change in healthcare. Big data, personalized care, digital medicine—it’s all a tidal wave of implications and opportunity. Even better, the new world of healthcare puts patients at the center.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We.&lt;/strong&gt; provides a breadth of communications services to clients across sectors including consumer health and wellness, health IT, medical devices, pharmaceuticals and life sciences. We develop innovative programs that reach and influence physicians, advocates, patients, regulators, policy makers, payors and the consumers at the center of it all.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This Account Executive, Health position is a hybrid in-office role (3x per week), based out of the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;We. Communication’s&lt;/strong&gt; New York City&lt;/em&gt; &lt;em&gt;office.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Account Management &amp;amp; Strategic Thinking&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct news monitoring and draft client-facing article summaries and recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain program and project action plans/timelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify opportunities for integration with media, digital and creative teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Media and Influencer Engagement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop targeted media lists and pitch angles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to media efforts, including pitching or research requests&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support influencer programs, including influencer audits, contracting and content development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to brainstorms &amp;amp; strategic campaign development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide timely and in-depth analysis of coverage results &amp;amp; trends&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Digital &amp;amp; Social Media Acumen&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in creating high-level digital/social media strategies that are integrated into communication plans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage with agency digital &amp;amp; monitoring divisions regarding client projects &amp;amp; deliverables&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Draft&amp;nbsp;content for amplifying&amp;nbsp;news on&amp;nbsp;client or executive social properties&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain social editorial calendars&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Client Engagement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Begin anticipating client communication challenges &amp;amp; develop recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to development &amp;amp; implementation of communication strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute tasks associated with projects; may lead certain aspects of project&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee client meeting agendas &amp;amp; recaps; own a speaking role on calls&lt;/li&gt;
