&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;About Us&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At &lt;strong&gt;We.&lt;/strong&gt;, we&#39;ve spent decades at the intersection of technology and humanity, bridging the gap between what businesses create and how people experience those creations. We&#39;ve learned that beneath even the most unruly situations — whether it&#39;s a global crisis, an emerging technology, or a sweeping organizational change—lies a simple human need. That need could be for trust, connection, safety, or a sense of purpose. But it’s always there. And it is only by uncovering these truths that we can make real, meaningful progress.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 class=&quot;iCIMS_InfoMsg iCIMS_InfoField_Job&quot;&gt;About The Role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;At WE, we believe that great people know great people. That&#39;s why we’re excited to introduce our Future Opportunities Referral program, designed for our valued employees to refer exceptional talent for future roles within our dynamic organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Why Refer?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Your referrals help us build a team of the sharpest minds in the business, ready to tell compelling stories and drive positive action. We appreciate your contribution to WE&#39;s growth and success by connecting us with individuals who share our passion and vision.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;How It Works&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;When you refer someone through this program, our Talent Acquisition team will review their background and skillset. As new opportunities arise, we&#39;ll reach out if there&#39;s a match. Your referral could be the next person to join our diverse and innovative team, working on intriguing projects and with some of the world&#39;s most exciting brands.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Our Commitment&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;At WE, we&#39;re all about celebrating diverse perspectives and elevating our people and their stories. We&#39;re committed to creating an inclusive culture where everyone feels free to bring their authentic selves to work. Your referrals help us continue this mission.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Thank You&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;We value your effort in referring great people to WE. Together, we can continue to build an environment where creativity thrives and where we can all achieve more, together.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
